      "text": " In this section, we fix notations and present some facts that are related to the question of solvability of Equation (3). Let  $\\mathbb{F}_q$  be a finite field of  $q$  elements where  $q$  is a power of the prime *p*. Fix a generator *g* of  $\\mathbb{F}_q^{\\times}$  and a proper divisor  $\\ell$  of  $q - 1$ . Let *L* be the subgroup of all  $\\ell$ -th power of elements of  $\\mathbb{F}_q^{\\times}$ . We have that  $\\mathbb{F}_q^{\\times}/L$  is generated by the coset  $gL$  and  $\\ell$  is the order of the cyclic group  $\\mathbb{F}_q^{\\times}/L$ .",
